Node.Notes: Uncertain. Tree assumes: With whom [things] are not like these. Apparently means something like: Who does not know such things?
Uncertain. Tree assumes something like: As one who calls to God and he answers him.
Apparently a righteous [and] blameless person [has become] a laughingstock.
Uncertain. Tree assumes something like: With respect to misfortune, contempt belongs the opinions of one who is at ease; [misfortune is] fixed for those whose feet slip.
Tree assumes something like: Understanding [is] with length of days.
Interpreted as to the disadvantage of those who are trusted.
